  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/c2c347fb7e63dc230a65177046b40d73.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/c2c347fb7e63dc230a65177046b40d73.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for the <strong>ULTIMATE</strong> bullet hell challenge! This shoot 'em up pushes your skills to the limit with relentless action, intricate bullet patterns, and intense boss fights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through a series of meticulously designed levels where every wave of enemies tests your reflexes and strategy. From dodging impossible barrages of bullets to facing off against bosses with unique and devastating attack patterns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/fa4400876f6c2bcbf48261a055f101f2.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/fa4400876f6c2bcbf48261a055f101f2.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who says shoot 'em up games are just about dodging bullets? In this game, <strong>you can absorb enemy projectiles</strong> of a specific type to gain energy. Use that energy to unleash the powerful ultra attack! But be careful—if you overheat, you <strong>might trigger an explosive disaster</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/f49796aa143ab8ccebd340969114dd7f.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/f49796aa143ab8ccebd340969114dd7f.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with players from around the world! Our Steam Leaderboard tracks your progress and high scores, allowing you to see how you stack up against the competition. Aim for the top, improve your skills, and show everyone who's the best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/7b91f092fb0768ee27ece88179f6e5c4.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/7b91f092fb0768ee27ece88179f6e5c4.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/2a76f3ccd603b75f22a5faaa27dde2d1.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/2a76f3ccd603b75f22a5faaa27dde2d1.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>  </strong><strong><br>CUSTOMIZE AND UPGRADE YOUR ARSENAL </strong>as you progress. Upgrade your weapons to suit your playstyle. Will you prioritize raw firepower, precision targeting, or defensive capabilities?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/d2fc7c4de042922a9a501816be7dfc2c.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/d2fc7c4de042922a9a501816be7dfc2c.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=166 /></span><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/d8eb5cc3dd29a197f8d3b3d98e9d92af.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/d8eb5cc3dd29a197f8d3b3d98e9d92af.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/ff7cd63144b74c211d38156679cceefd.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/ff7cd63144b74c211d38156679cceefd.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WHETHER YOU'RE A SEASONED BULLET HELL VETERAN OR A DARING NEWCOMER,</strong> the game offers an easy start which turns into a brutal yet rewarding experience with your progress. Stunning visuals, a high-energy soundtrack, and carefully crafted gameplay combine to create an unforgettable experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to face the chaos, master the patterns, and prove your skill? The ultimate challenge awaits!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/c2c347fb7e63dc230a65177046b40d73.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/c2c347fb7e63dc230a65177046b40d73.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for the <strong>ULTIMATE</strong> bullet hell challenge! This shoot 'em up pushes your skills to the limit with relentless action, intricate bullet patterns, and intense boss fights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through a series of meticulously designed levels where every wave of enemies tests your reflexes and strategy. From dodging impossible barrages of bullets to facing off against bosses with unique and devastating attack patterns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/fa4400876f6c2bcbf48261a055f101f2.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/fa4400876f6c2bcbf48261a055f101f2.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who says shoot 'em up games are just about dodging bullets? In this game, <strong>you can absorb enemy projectiles</strong> of a specific type to gain energy. Use that energy to unleash the powerful ultra attack! But be careful—if you overheat, you <strong>might trigger an explosive disaster</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/f49796aa143ab8ccebd340969114dd7f.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/f49796aa143ab8ccebd340969114dd7f.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with players from around the world! Our Steam Leaderboard tracks your progress and high scores, allowing you to see how you stack up against the competition. Aim for the top, improve your skills, and show everyone who's the best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/7b91f092fb0768ee27ece88179f6e5c4.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/7b91f092fb0768ee27ece88179f6e5c4.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/2a76f3ccd603b75f22a5faaa27dde2d1.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/2a76f3ccd603b75f22a5faaa27dde2d1.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>  </strong><strong><br>CUSTOMIZE AND UPGRADE YOUR ARSENAL </strong>as you progress. Upgrade your weapons to suit your playstyle. Will you prioritize raw firepower, precision targeting, or defensive capabilities?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/d2fc7c4de042922a9a501816be7dfc2c.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/d2fc7c4de042922a9a501816be7dfc2c.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=166 /></span><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/d8eb5cc3dd29a197f8d3b3d98e9d92af.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/d8eb5cc3dd29a197f8d3b3d98e9d92af.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras/ff7cd63144b74c211d38156679cceefd.avif?t=1737401293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355060/extras_big/ff7cd63144b74c211d38156679cceefd.avif?t=1737401293 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WHETHER YOU'RE A SEASONED BULLET HELL VETERAN OR A DARING NEWCOMER,</strong> the game offers an easy start which turns into a brutal yet rewarding experience with your progress. Stunning visuals, a high-energy soundtrack, and carefully crafted gameplay combine to create an unforgettable experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to face the chaos, master the patterns, and prove your skill? The ultimate challenge awaits!</p>",
